        <p>MacPher­son is one of Sin­ga­pore’s oldest Hous­ing Board es­tates, but it has kept up with the times with a chic new paint scheme.</p>
        <p>Block 53 Pipit Road (above), which was built in 1985, has an un­usual de­sign. Though it looks like two blocks fac­ing each other, it is ac­tu­ally one U-shaped block with a shorter con­nect­ing sec­tion.</p>

